&lt;NEW&gt;

The seeker scrambled to his feet holding his weapon out in front of him
almost like a shield as he stumbled back.

He looked at Trelos quizzically, as if he had expected him to be
unconscious, stunned and ready for transport, but instead Trelos is just
shaking it off. He took a brief look at his two companions, neither of whom
look to be in operational condition. He then turned back to face Trelos a
look of fear tracing itself across his face.

With a brief nod he leaped into the air, transformed into his seeker mode,
it was obvious this soldier had had enough. With a sputter and then flare
from his engines he began to climb into the skies attempting to leave Trelos
and this city behind!

